NAME
    Text::Pivot - Partition text around a pivot (like 'split' but with more
    control and flexibility)

VERSION
    version 0.0010

SYNOPSIS
        my $pivot = Text::Pivot->new( ... )

AUTHOR
      Robert Krimen <robertkrimen@gmail.com>

